Application role Dagflow role Can do <code>APP_VIEWER</code> <code>VIEWER</code> Open the UI and read Dagster state. <code>APP_LAUNCHER</code> <code>LAUNCHER</code> Launch, reexecute, terminate, and delete runs. <code>APP_EDITOR</code> <code>EDITOR</code> Manage schedules, sensors, backfills, assets, dynamic partitions, concurrency, PEX code-location versions, and single code-location reloads. <code>APP_ADMIN</code> <code>ADMIN</code> Add, remove, globally reload, or shut down code locations and call app admin procedures. <p>Admin grant example:</p> <pre><code>GRANT APPLICATION ROLE dagflow_app.APP_VIEWER TO ROLE analyst;
GRANT APPLICATION ROLE dagflow_app.APP_LAUNCHER TO ROLE service_runner;
GRANT APPLICATION ROLE dagflow_app.APP_EDITOR TO ROLE data_engineer;
GRANT APPLICATION ROLE dagflow_app.APP_ADMIN TO ROLE platform_admin;
</code></pre>
